Package project2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    The Account class is an abstract class that is used to create different types of bank account subclasses.
    AccountDatabase
    The AccountDatabase class stores accounts in an array and provides methods to access and manipulate those accounts.
    Checking
    This class is an object class used to create a checkings accounts that can then be added into the account data base.
    CheckingTest
    Test class for JUnit testing of Checking.monthlyInterest() and Checking.monthlyFee().
    Date
    The Date class stores information about dates.
    DateTest
    Test class for JUnit testing of Date.isValid().
    MoneyMarket
    This class is an object class used to create a money market account that can then be added into the account database.
    MoneyMarketTest
    Test class for JUnit testing of MoneyMarket.monthlyInterest() and MoneyMarket.monthlyFee().
    Profile
    The Profile class holds the first and last names of potential account holders.
    RunProject2
    Runs the project.
    Savings
    This class is an object class used to create a savings accounts that can then be added into the account data base.
    TransactionManager
    The TransactionManager class is the I/O handler for manipulating data about the bank accounts.
